00:49:38.910 --> 00:49:41.827
Kur ju jeni nje lum i vogel i paket, ne rregull,

00:49:42.202 --> 00:49:45.994
por tani ju jeni bere oqeani, keshtu behuni oqeani.

00:49:46.369 --> 00:49:47.952
Kur ju beheni deti, beheni deti

00:49:48.244 --> 00:49:50.452
Kur ju beheni oqeani, beheni oqeani.

00:49:50.785 --> 00:49:52.618
Nje det nuk mund te qendroje i paket.

